<style>
  .product_faq {
    background: #3C1F1B;
  }
  .product_faq-wrapper {
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 50px;
  }
  .product_faq-text {
    width: 515px;
  }
  .product_faq-text h2, .product_faq-text p {
    color: #F2F2EA;
  }
  .product_faq-text p {
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .product_faq-items {
    width: calc(100% - 565px);
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .product_faq-item {
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    transition: 0.3s;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 4px 40px;
  }
  .product_faq-item:hover {
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .product_faq-item-title {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 16px 0px;
  }
  .product_faq-item-title p {
    max-width: calc(100% - 38px);
  }
  a.product_faq-item-cross {
    display: block;
    height: max-content;
  }
  .product_faq-item-title a svg {
      height: 28px;
      width: auto;
      transition: .3s;
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    display: block;
  }
  .product_faq-item-title a svg path {
    transition: .3s;
  }
  .product_faq-item.active .product_faq-item-title a svg {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
  }
  .product_faq-item.active .product_faq-item-title a svg path {
    stroke: #F24F14;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text {
    height: max-content;
    max-height: 0px;
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 100%;
    transition: .5s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    transition: .3s;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text a:hover {
    opacity: .85;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text a:active {
    opacity: .7;
  }
  .product_faq-item.active .product_faq-item-text {
    padding-top: 21px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    max-height: 250px;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text::before {
    content:'';
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    max-height: 0px;
    width: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0px;
    left: 0;
    background: rgba(60, 31, 27, 0.30);
    transition: .5s;
  }
  .product_faq-item-text::before {
    max-height: 1px;
  }
  .product_faq-desc {
    margin-top: 15px;
  }
  .product_faq-btns {
    margin-top: 30px;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .product_faq-btns a {
    margin: 0;
  }
  .product_faq-a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .product_faq-btns-desktop-hidden {
    display: none;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .product_faq-item {
        padding: 4px 30px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .product_faq-btns-mobile-hidden {
      display: none;
    }
    .product_faq-btns-desktop-hidden {
      display: flex!important;
    }
    .product_faq-items {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .product_faq-btns {
      margin-top: 0;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .product_faq-text {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .product_faq-wrapper {
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .product_faq {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    .product_faq-wrapper a.rebranding_btn {
      margin: 0px auto;
    }
    .product_faq-item-title {
      padding: 15px 0;
    }
    .product_faq-item {
        padding: 0px 20px;
    }
    .product_faq-item.active .product_faq-item-text {
    padding-top: 15px;
    padding-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .product_faq-item-title a svg {
      height: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="container rebranding_container">
  <div class="product_faq-wrapper block-flex-wrap">
    <div class="product_faq-text">
      <h2 class="h2-heading-ss">
        Featured
        <span class="h2-heading-pp">questions</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="product_faq-desc body-text">
        Have more questions? Visit our <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en" target="_blank" class="product_faq-a standart-hover">Help Center</a>
      </p>
      <div class="product_faq-btns block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 product_faq-btns-mobile-hidden">
        <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en" target="_blank" class="rebranding_btn">
        Help Center
      </a>
        <a href="#product_boxes" class="rebranding_btn rebranding_btn-main product_authenticate-now-btn-track">
        Authenticate now
      </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="product_faq-items block-flex-wrap">
      <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">How Does LegitGrails Authentication Work?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            LegitGrails provides a seamless authentication process for Chrome Hearts items, combining cutting-edge AI technology with expert human analysis for over 99.3% accuracy. Simply select your item category and preferred response time on our platform to get started. 
<br><br>Next, upload clear, high-quality images of your item, including labels, engravings, and any distinctive details. Our system processes these images, and our specialists carefully verify the results. You’ll receive a detailed verdict and a personalized certificate of authenticity, giving you complete confidence in your Chrome Hearts piece.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">How Long Does LegitGrails Authentication Take?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            We know how important fast authentication is. LegitGrails offers flexible response times, including 12 hours, 6 hours, 2 hours, or even as fast as 30 minutes. Simply choose the best option for you, and our team will ensure your Chrome Hearts item is authenticated promptly and accurately.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">What Makes Chrome Hearts a Luxury Brand, and Is It Made of Real Silver?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Chrome Hearts is considered a luxury brand due to its exceptional craftsmanship, exclusive designs, and use of premium materials. Every piece is meticulously handcrafted using high-quality sterling silver, gold, and precious stones. 
<br><br>The brand’s dedication to artisanal techniques and limited production ensures both exclusivity and superior quality, justifying its premium price. Many Chrome Hearts accessories and jewelry pieces are indeed made from genuine sterling silver, adding to their lasting value and appeal.
</p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Who Founded Chrome Hearts, and Who Owns It Today?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Chrome Hearts was founded in 1988 by Richard Stark, John Bowman, and Leonard Kamhout in Los Angeles, California. Initially focused on leather motorcycle gear and silver accessories for the biker community, the brand quickly gained a cult following among celebrities and fashion insiders. 
<br><br>Today, Chrome Hearts remains a family-owned business, with Richard Stark and his wife, Laurie Lynn Stark, leading the brand. Their children are also actively involved, ensuring its legacy continues.
</p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">When Was Chrome Hearts Founded, and How Did It Start?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Founded in 1988, Chrome Hearts began as a small operation in a Los Angeles garage. Richard Stark, a leather dealer, partnered with John Bowman, a leather manufacturer, and Leonard Kamhout, a master silversmith, to create high-quality leather motorcycle gear and silver accessories. Their unique craftsmanship quickly caught the attention of rock stars and fashion influencers, propelling the brand into the luxury fashion scene.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Does Chrome Hearts Have Religious or Christian Symbolism?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
           Chrome Hearts draws inspiration from Gothic and medieval aesthetics, frequently incorporating crosses, fleur-de-lis, and other symbolic motifs. 
<br><br>While some of these elements have Christian origins, the brand primarily uses them for their artistic and stylistic impact rather than religious significance. This fusion of historical symbolism with modern luxury contributes to Chrome Hearts’ edgy and distinctive appeal.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">Why Is Chrome Hearts a Cult-Favorite Luxury Brand?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
            Chrome Hearts has built a cult following by merging high-end craftsmanship with rebellious, rock-and-roll-inspired designs. Its dedication to quality, exclusivity, and handcrafted production attracts fashion enthusiasts seeking unique, statement pieces. 
<br><br>The brand’s collaborations with celebrities, musicians, and artists – combined with a low-profile marketing strategy that avoids traditional advertising – have only heightened its desirability and mystique.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="product_faq-item">
        <div class="product_faq-item-title">
          <p class="body-text">What Is the Signature Chrome Hearts Font and Its History?</p>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="product_faq-item-cross">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M14 1.94116V25.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M2 13.9412L26 13.9412" stroke="#3C1F1B" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="product_faq-item-text">
          <p class="small-text">
           The Chrome Hearts logo features a distinctive Gothic-inspired typeface reminiscent of Old English script. This font choice perfectly complements the brand’s aesthetic, reinforcing its medieval and countercultural influences. 
<br><br>The specific typeface resembles Cloister Black, a classic blackletter font known for its ornate, intricate letterforms. This unique typography is a key element of Chrome Hearts’ identity, adding to its bold and rebellious luxury appeal.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      <div class="product_faq-btns block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 product_faq-btns-desktop-hidden">
        <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en" target="_blank" class="rebranding_btn">
        Help Center
      </a>
        <a href="#product_boxes" class="rebranding_btn rebranding_btn-main product_authenticate-now-btn-track">
        Authenticate now
      </a>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
              
